===========================================================================
$NetBSD$

Copy ppp.conf from ${PREFIX}/share/examples/${PKGBASE} to 
${PKG_SYSCONFBASE}/ppp and modify these to suit to your needs :

. vpi/vci
. login/password
. vid2/pid2

You will find your vid1, pid1, vid2 and pid2 here :

${PREFIX}/share/${PKGBASE}/modems.db

